item.description:
@xx_matty_xx wrote:

make sure server is not already running. if it’s not running then restart da computer. you can usually restart by clicking start and shutdown. when it says it is now safe to turn off your computer wait a few seconds and push the power button again. it might take a minute or so to come back on.
